reviewText: I showed this video at our monthly church function and it was a big hit because normally most of the folks that come to our diners and entertainment leave after the first 15 or 20 minutes but no one left everyone stayed and watched this video until it was finished. Amazon has never let me down when I needed them to come through for me. I needed a great video because I was in charge of entertainment and I received Kudo's for coming up with a winner, Thank You Amazon. for not letting me down!!!
